            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德勝(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8048:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8048\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8048-TW</a>)20日09:24上漲5.3元，股價漲停報58.8元，委買491,000張，成交892張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為光纖網路局端、用戶端設備及網管交換器之研發製造及買賣。室外無線網路之研發製造及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德勝(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8048:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8048\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8048-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲14.81%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.68%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-7 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-24 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+17 張</li> <li>融資增減：+647 張</li> <li>融券增減：+14 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
